Remove roam-style tags
#+begin_src emacs-lisp
  ,#+ROAM_TAGS: foo bar
  ,#+ROAM_ALIASES: baz
  ,#+ROAM_REFS: https://example.com
#+end_src

For standard org tags
#+begin_src emacs-lisp
  ,#+filetags: foo bar
#+end_src

filetags can go right under title.

